The glomerular membrane consists of [[mesangial_cell|mesangial cell]]s, modified pericytes that in other parts of the body separate capillaries from each other. The podocytes adjoining them have filtration slits of diameter 25 nm that are formed by the pseudopodia arising from them. The filtration slits are covered by a diaphragm that includes the transmembrane protein [[nephrin|nephrin]].
腎小球膜由腎小球系膜細胞，改性週細胞在體內分離毛細管彼此的其它部分。毗鄰他們足有直徑25納米是由他們引起的偽足形成過濾縫隙。過濾狹縫覆蓋有隔膜，其包括跨膜蛋白腎病蛋白。-->

==病理==<!--
[[Image:Membranous_nephropathy_-_cropped_-_mpas_-_very_high_mag.jpg|thumb]]顯示在[[膜性腎小球腎炎|膜性腎小球腎炎]]GBM的"尖状"(spike)形成。{{link-en|MPAS染色|Jones' stain}}.]]

* [[Goodpasture's_syndrome|Goodpasture's syndrome]] is also known as "anti-glomerular basement membrane disease". Capillaries become inflamed as a result of damage to the basement membrane by [[antibodies|antibodies]] to alpha 3 NC1 domain of type IV collagen. 
Goodpasture綜合症也被稱為“抗腎小球基底膜病”。毛細血管發炎作為基底膜損傷由抗體的IV型膠原α3 NC1區的結果。

* [[Nephrotic_syndrome|Nephrotic syndrome]] is a change in the structure of the glomerular filtration mechanism usually in the glomerular basement membrane. Some symptoms include [[proteinuria|proteinuria]], [[hypoalbuminaemia|hypoalbuminaemia]], [[oedema|oedema]], and [[hyperlipidemia|hyperlipidemia]].
腎病綜合徵是腎小球濾過機制通常在腎小球基底膜的結構變化。有些症狀包括蛋白尿，低白蛋白血症，水腫和高脂血症。

* Diabetic [[glomerulosclerosis|glomerulosclerosis]] is a thickening of the basement membrane, which can become up to 4-5 times thicker than normal. Can be caused by [[insulin|insulin deficiency]] or resultant [[hyperglycemia|hyperglycemia]].
糖尿病性腎小球硬化症是基底膜，從而可以成為高達4-5倍，比正常更厚的增厚。可通過胰島素缺乏或所得的高血糖症引起的。

* [[Alport_syndrome|Alport syndrome]] is a X-linked hereditary nephritis caused by mutations in type IV collagen, leading to a split lamina densa of the glomerular basement membrane. It also affects the eye and inner ear.
Alport綜合徵是一種由IV型膠原突變X連鎖遺傳性腎炎，導致腎小球基底膜的一個裂開緻密板。它也影響眼部和內耳。-->

